1814     // The guard for FC0 is updated to guard both FC0 and FC1. This is done by
1815     // changing the NonLoopGuardBlock for FC0 to the NonLoopGuardBlock for FC1.
1816     // Thus, one path from the guard goes to the preheader for FC0 (and thus
